_sText:
My idea for a winter type map, but I got further into Zombie mod so I didn't feel like continuing with it. This MiP includes the following:

HDR ready
Snow
Cubemaps
3D Skybox already made

I already added settings to the Env_Sun and Light_enviroment which I think make the map look good.

You can easily change around spawnpoint, geometry, and settings if you want.

So yeah, do what want with this one, I'd look at improving my displacements though, seeing as it was my first time using them =o
